  "remarks": "Co-owner with Boris ROTENBERG of Stroygazmontazh Corporation (or SGM Group).  Close financial associate of President Putin.  Since March 2014, has made billions of dollars through contracts from Gazprom and the Sochi Olympics awarded by Putin.  SGM Group won a major tender for the construction of the Kerch bridge that links Crimea to mainland Russia; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (relisted on 16 Jun. 2017 and 10 June 2023)",
